{"tid":2194489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局去信官校　冀盡快呼籲學生及家長參加普及檢測","createTime":"2020-09-08T13:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T14:00:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17b638d2e4c8f8d8b7f3114b2dbcb93fc9139654","tid":2194489,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:59:50.000Z","msg":"教育局致函所有官立小學及中學校長，希望校長盡快發家長信，呼籲學生、家長及家人積極參加普及社區檢測，並附上家長信範本。<br />\n<br />\n範本提及普及社區檢測計劃為找出隱形患者，切斷傳播鏈，希望家長把握未來數天，安排子女及家人參加，為恢復面授課堂締造有利條件。<br />\n<br />\n教育局亦在信中感謝廿四所官立學校借出校舍，作為普及檢測場地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=404815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404815&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNbyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=ea44a900\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404815&h=8d42447e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=404815</a>"},{"pid":"42b5f4df041d9b26f35af6577a70efde084898f0","tid":2194489,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"Move to SPAM"}]}